lines.text: Wake up, Rita! What do you think those two do after work, wash glasses?
What about you? You almost mowed a family down on the lake!
They don't give you 10 to 15 for that.
I'm sorry Mother, God was only able to create *one* perfect daughter for you, now you'll just have to suffer with me.
Wow, these are all French designs. Coco Channel...
It's pronounced Coco *Chanel*. And I don't share my clothes.
